title: Altamont and Mandy-Lyn Present: Rock N’ Roll Suicides
description:
Altamont is proud to introduce our newest collaboration with Mandy-Lyn, Rock N’ Roll Suicides: http://altamontapparel.com/contributo...

This is a series of tees where Mandy-Lyn recreated some of the most iconic suicides in rock music including, GG Allin, Kurt Cobain, and Sid Vicious, using her favorite subjects, beautiful women.
